{"lemma":"صِحَّةٌ","slug":"صِحَّةٌ","root":"ص.ح.ح","root_slug":"ص-ح-ح","root_link":"/words/roots/ص-ح-ح","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":7},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n23761"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B5%D9%90%D8%AD%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%A9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"health","examples":[{"text":"الصِّحَّةُ تَاجٌ عَلَى رُؤُوسِ الْأَصِحَّاءِ لَا يَرَاهُ إِلَّا الْمَرْضَى.","english":"Health is a crown on the heads of the healthy, that only the ill can see."},{"text":"آلَةُ الْعَيشِ صِحَّةٌ وَشَبَابٌ / فَإِذَا وَلَّيَا عَنِ الْمَرءِ وَلَّى"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"soundness, wholeness, correctness"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"completeness"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"good condition"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"validity"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"God bless you!, bless you! (exclamation said when someone sneezes)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"Cheers!, To your health! (said in a toast, before drinking)"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/sˤiħ.ħa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n23761","headword_ar":"صِحَّةٌ","root":"SH","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, MA, O, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuH~N","text_ar":"صُحٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * O, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaHaAHN","text_ar":"صَحَاحٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K) [all app. inf. ns., of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaH~a","text_ar":"صَحَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.; and used as simple substs. meaning]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Health,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"soundness of body;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, MA, O;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suqomN","text_ar":"سُقْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saqamN","text_ar":"سَقَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, A, O:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"departure of disease:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SiH~apN","text_ar":"صِحَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is said to be in the body and in religion; like as are [its contrs.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maraDN","text_ar":"مَرَضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suqomN","text_ar":"سُقْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Aboo-Is-hák, TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mrD","text_ar":"مرض"},{"kind":"text","text":":) in the body, it is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a natural state"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"condition, wherewith the actions"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and functions"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the body have the natural course:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and it is metaphorically used in relation to [other things, including] attributes, or ideal things: (Msb:) and signifies ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a sound, valid, substantial, real, sure, certain, true, right, correct, just"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"proper, whole"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"entire, state"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"condition;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as is indicated in the first paragraph of this art.; or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"freedom from every imperfection"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"defect"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fault"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"blemish,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and from everything that would occasion doubt"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"suspicion"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"evil opinion."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, TA.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^awoSaY fiY SiH~atihi wa$iH~atihi","text_ar":"اَوْصَى فِى صِحَّتِهِ وَشِحَّتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$H","text_ar":"شح"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wasuqomihi","text_ar":"وَسُقْمِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAna *`lika fiY SuH~ihi","text_ar":"كَانَ ذٰلِكَ فِى صُحِّهِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"That was in his state of health,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"soundness, and his illness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sickness"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (AO, S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mina","text_ar":"مِنَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA A^aqoraba AlS~aHaAHa","text_ar":"مَا اَقْرَبَ الصَّحَاحَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~aqaAmi","text_ar":"السَّقَامِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"How little removed is health,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"soundness, from illness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sickness!"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (O.)"}],"source_refs":["S","A","MA","O","K","Msb","L","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}